Start.
Read day, month, and year from the user.
If year ≤ 0    → Print "Invalid Date"    → Stop
If month < 1 OR month > 12    → Print "Invalid Date"    → Stop
If (year % 400 == 0)    → Set leap = True
Else if (year % 100 == 0)    → Set leap = False
Else if (year % 4 == 0)    → Set leap = True
Else    → Set leap = False
If month is 1, 3, 5, 7, 8, 10, or 12    → Set max_day = 31
Else if month is 4, 6, 9, or 11    → Set max_day = 30
Else if month == 2    → If leap == True      → Set max_day = 29    → Else      → Set max_day = 28
If day < 1 OR day > max_day    → Print "Invalid Date"    → Stop
Increment day by 1
If day > max_day    → Set day = 1    → Increment month by 1
If month > 12    → Set month = 1    → Increment year by 1
Print "Next Date is: day/month/year"
Stop.
